{"lemma": "بَصِيرَةٌ", "slug": "بَصِيرَةٌ", "root": "ب.ص.ر", "root_slug": "ب-ص-ر", "root_link": "/words/roots/ب-ص-ر", "pos": "N", "pos_camel": "noun", "paradigm": [], "frequency_in_corpus": 0, "cross_references": {"qac": {"found": true, "lemma_key": "بَصِيرَة", "root": "بصر", "pos": "N", "occurrence_count": 7}, "wiktextract": {"found": true, "entry_count": 1, "pos_tags": ["noun"], "has_etymology": false, "sense_count": 3}, "lanes": {"found": true, "entry_ids": ["n2652"], "search_url": "https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%B5%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}}, "translations": {"en": "mental perception", "fa": "ادراک ذهنی", "ur": "ذہنی ادراک", "tr": "zihinsel algı", "id": "persepsi mental", "bn": "মানসিক উপলব্ধি", "es": "percepción mental", "fr": "perception mentale", "de": "geistige Wahrnehmung", "ru": "умственное восприятие", "zh": "心智感知"}, "definition": {"source": "wiktextract", "senses": [{"pos": "noun", "gloss": "the faculty of mental perception"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "discernment, sagacity, insight"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "circumspection, watchfulness"}]}, "etymology": null, "ipa": ["/ba.sˤiː.ra/"], "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n2652", "headword_ar": "بَصِيرَةٌ", "root": "bSr", "body": [{"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Mental perception;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "perceptive faculty of the mind;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baSarN", "text_ar": "بَصَرٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (B:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "knowledge;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb;) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baSarN", "text_ar": "بَصَرٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Msb) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AisotiboSaArN", "text_ar": "اِسْتِبْصَارٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (Msb:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "understanding; intelligence; skill:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K:)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlbaSiyrapu", "text_ar": "البَصِيرَةُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlAi sotiboSaAru fiY Al$~aYo'i", "text_ar": "الاِ سْتِبْصَارُ فِى الشَّىْءِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[which implies all the meanings above: see 10]: (S:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Alqalobi", "text_ar": "القَلْبِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baSaru", "text_ar": "بَصَرُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[in like manner] signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "mental perception"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "vision"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "view; idea,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "opinion, occurring to the mind:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K:) the pl. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baSiyrapN", "text_ar": "بَصِيرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baSaAy^ru", "text_ar": "بَصَايرُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (M, B;) and the pl. of ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baSarN", "text_ar": "بَصَرٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", as syn. therewith,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aboSaArN", "text_ar": "اَبْصَارٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (B.) [Sometimes it is opposed to"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baSarN", "text_ar": "بَصَرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", as in the first and second of the following exs.]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ahuwnu mino EimaY AlbaSaAy^iri", "text_ar": "اَهُونُ مِنْ عِمَى البَصَايِرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EamaY AlA^aboSaAri", "text_ar": "عَمَى الاَبْصَارِ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Blindness of the eyes is a lighter thing than blindness of the perceptive faculties of the mind"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (A.) When Mo'áwiyeh said to Ibn-'Abbás,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yaAbaniY", "text_ar": "يَابَنِى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "haA$imK tuSaAbuwna fiY A^aboSaArikumo", "text_ar": "هَاشِمٍ تُصَابُونَ فِى اَبْصَارِكُمْ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "O sons of Háshim, ye are afflicted in your eyes"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "], the latter replied,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "waA^anotumo yaA baniY A^umay~apa tuSaAbuwna fiY baSaAy^irikumo", "text_ar": "وَاَنْتُمْ يَا بَنِى اُمَيَّةَ تُصَابُونَ فِى بَصَايِرِكُمْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "And ye, O sons of Umeiyeh, are afflicted in your perceptive faculties of the mind"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (M.) And the Arabs say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aEomaY A@ll~`hu baSaAy^irapu", "text_ar": "اَعْمَى ا@للّٰهُ بَصَايِرَةُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "May God blind his faculties of understanding!"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "And one says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lahu firaAsapN *aAtu baSiyrapK", "text_ar": "لَهُ فِرَاسَةٌ ذَاتُ بَصِيرَةٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baSaAy^ira", "text_ar": "بَصَايِرَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He possesses true intuitive perception."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "raA^ayotu Ealayoka", "text_ar": "رَاَيْتُ عَلَيْكَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "*aAta AlbaSaAy^iri", "text_ar": "ذَاتَ البَصَايِرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I saw"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "impressed"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "upon thee the signs of perceptive faculties of the mind"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (A.) ―         -b2-  Also"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Belief,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "firm belief, of the heart,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "mind."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaY baSiyrapK", "text_ar": "عَلَى بَصِيرَةٍ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "According to,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "agreeably with, knowledge and assurance:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "purposely; intentionally."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaY gayori baSiyrapK", "text_ar": "عَلَى غَيْرِ بَصِيرَةٍ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Without certainty."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, TA.) ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Constancy,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "firmness, in religion."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) ―         -b4-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "An evidence, a testimony, a proof, an argument,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the like;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maboSarapN", "text_ar": "مَبْصَرَةٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maboSarN", "text_ar": "مَبْصَرٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (K.) ―         -b5-  [And hence,]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Blood,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "somewhat thereof,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(As, S, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "by which one is directed to an animal that has been shot,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to the knowledge thereof:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(As, AA, S, M, K:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "blood upon the ground;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(AZ, S;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "what sticks upon the ground, not upon the body:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M:) what adheres to the body is termed"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jadiy~apN", "text_ar": "جَدِيَّةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (AZ, S:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a portion of blood of the size of a dirhem:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "what is of a round form, like a shield:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "what is of an oblong form:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "what is of the size of the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "firosin", "text_ar": "فِرْسِن"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "foot"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the camel:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in all these explanations, blood being meant: or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "blood not flowing:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "what flows thereof at one single time:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a portion of blood that glistens:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(B:) and (as some say, M) the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "blood of a virgin:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K:) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "blood-revenge:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a fine for homicide:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baSaAy^iru", "text_ar": "بَصَايِرُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", as above: (S, M:) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baSiyrN", "text_ar": "بَصِيرٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", which occurs in a verse cited by AHn, may also be a pl. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baSiyrapN", "text_ar": "بَصِيرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", applied to blood, [or rather a coll. gen. n., of which"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bSyrp", "text_ar": "بصيرة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is the n. un.,] like as"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$aEiyrN", "text_ar": "شَعِيرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$aEiyrapN", "text_ar": "شَعِيرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; or it may be for"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bSyrp", "text_ar": "بصيرة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "p", "text_ar": "ة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "being elided by poetic license; or it may be a dial. var. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bSyrp", "text_ar": "بصيرة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", like as one says"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bayaADN", "text_ar": "بَيَاضٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bayaADapN", "text_ar": "بَيَاضَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (M.) ElAs'ar El-Joafee says,"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "raAHwA baSaAy^iruhumo EalaY A^akotaAfihimo\n                      \n                     \n                        wabaSiyratiY yaEoduw bihaA EatadN waA^aY"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They went with their blood upon their shoulderblades; but my blood, a ready and swift and strong horse runs with it"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; meaning, they neglected the blood of their father, and left it behind them; i. e., they did not take revenge for it; but I have sought my blood-revenge: (S, M: *) but see another explanation in what follows. (S. [See also Ham p. 59.]) ―         -b6-  (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A witness:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Lh, S, * M, Mgh, K:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "an observer and a witness."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A.)"}], "source_refs": ["B", "S", "Msb", "M", "K", "TA", "As", "AA", "AZ"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}